# CHANGELOG

## 0.1.5 - 2025/06/12
- Added background/text to user preferences

## 0.1.4 - 2025/04/12
- Added ability to track moods hourly
- Added generic notes field
- Added user preferences
- Added ability to disable predictions

## 0.1.3 - 2025/04/08
- Fixed prediction dates being one day short
- Move buttons to bottom of screen
- Add counter with days remaining/to go
- Stop predicted days appearing in the previous month on the calendar
- Fix issues with DST
- Fix issues with native import giving false errors
- Remove support for legacy native format
- Make text bigger
- Make buttons bigger and add more space around buttons

## 0.1.2 - 2025/02/09
- Added mood and flow markers
- Fixed daylight savings time bug
- Updated menu layout
- Hide menu on startup

## 0.1.1 - 2025/01/13
- Improved predictions
- Some formatting updates e.g. highlighting only today's date
- External formats for imports

## 0.1.0 - 2024/12/14
- Initial version
